TI  - Are cross-border classes feasible for students to collaborate in the analysis of energy efficiency strategies for socioeconomic development while keeping CO2 concentration controlled?
PY  - 2021
T2  - Sustainability (Switzerland)
VL  - 13
IS  - 3
